{
  "stem": "17625.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 154.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I learned they were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came from Bialystok, from Lomza.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came from-- from-- Markowa, and from other towns there-- there-- from Grodno.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This transport came by the end of the year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they filled up-- where we-- I came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They stood there already for two months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why-- why-- why did they stay for two months?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Before then, there was a commander, which they killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They gassed them all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They killed them all off, so they took a new commander.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some-- sometime-- something I heard, that [SIGHS] they planned something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't plan something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whatever it was-- reasons-- there's plenty of reasons for doing this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Am I-- am I-- am I too far away?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This commander was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came home from the-- from the-- and they changed-- day shift, night shift; bunker one, bunker two; bunker two, bunker one; day and night for shifts, hundreds of people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were busy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All Jews?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All Jews-- only Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [SIGHS] us they didn't call in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For us, they make our commander, the 10 or 12 people, whatever it was, and they took us in in Birkenau in a-- in a new building, a crematorium two.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Auschwitz was crematorium one, and this one, they built a big crematorium, crematorium two.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what they send us to-- to Auschwitz, to learn the trade-- the ovens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the other ones-- we wanted bunkers, which were-- they throw the two-- they-- the-- the-- the people in-- into this here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they-- they had to empty out the-- this, because the-- the-- the earth was-- was-- was-- was-- was-- was turning back with-- with-- with the bodies.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were swollen in summertime-- big troubles.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
